data.description:
SELLING AS-IS. We are motivated to sell!!
This clean, country home is 1740 sq ft, 3 BR, 2 BA on large corner lot. Master Bedroom has walk-in closet and large bathroom with whirlpool tub and separate shower. Large Eat-in Kitchen with black appliances. Large Living Room with trey ceiling feature. Fenced in back yard with large workshop/shed. This is a lot of house for a little money.
New HVAC/Ducts-2009
New Carpet-2009
New Water Heater-2010
New Laminate Wood Floors-2010
New Roof-2011
New Exterior Doors-2013 & 2014
New HE/Storm Windows-2015
data.whatILove: Large, open rooms. Upgraded features (HVAC, Windows, Doors, Roof, Floors, etc). Quiet, country neighborhood but convenient to amenities. Great schools. Fenced backyard. New shed.
